      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Clean, honest car that\u2019s a great budget-friendly way to get on the road. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it starts, moves, and offers solid value for someone who wants affordable transportation or a handy project to tinker with. Priced fairly for a straightforward sale, and I\u2019m happy to answer questions so you know exactly what you\u2019re getting.",
