      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-focused car with solid bones and plenty of mechanical upside. Runs, moves, and delivers the kind of analog feel enthusiasts appreciate, with an engine that pulls cleanly and a chassis that still feels composed. Cosmetic wear and age-related needs are present, so it\u2019s best suited for someone who wants an affordable project, shop car, or budget daily with character. A great chance to get into a capable platform without spending big money.",
