    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with real personality, this ride has the kind of lived-in charm that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s an ideal pick for someone who appreciates character and sees opportunity where others just see age\u2014a perfect canvas for a daily driver, weekend tinkering project, or budget-friendly set of wheels with unmistakable presence. If you want something affordable, distinctive, and full of potential, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 6950.0,
