    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready to serve as practical transportation, this vehicle offers a straightforward opportunity for the next owner. It shows its age and would benefit from some TLC, but it presents strong value for someone seeking an affordable commuter, project, or backup vehicle. Priced to move and sold as-is.",
