    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation, a project, or a handy extra vehicle. It has the honest wear you\u2019d expect from an older used car, but it still offers good value at this price and could be a great fit for someone who doesn\u2019t mind a little TLC. Priced to sell and worth a look if you want something cheap and straightforward.",
